{
  "title": "Home IDS 🛡️ Tier 1: Master Triage Hub (Ultimate SOC Edition)",
  "uid": "ids-master-hub-ultimate",
  "tags": ["ids", "hub", "soc", "showcase", "production"],
  "timezone": "browser",
  "refresh": "10s",
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "name": "PROMETHEUS_DS",
        "type": "datasource",
        "query": "prometheus",
        "label": "Prometheus Source"
      },
      {
        "name": "LOKI_DS",
        "type": "datasource",
        "query": "loki",
        "label": "Loki Source"
      }
    ]
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "title": "Navigation Matrix",
      "gridPos": { "h": 2, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "transparent": true,
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### **🧭 Triage Hub** | [📊 DNS & ML Diagnostics](/d/ids-tier2-dns/home-ids-tier-2-dns-ml-diagnostics?var-device=.*) | [🔒 Network & Lateral (Zeek NDR)](/d/ids-tier2-ndr/home-ids-tier-2-network-lateral-zeek-ndr?var-device=.*) | [🌍 GeoIP & OSINT Intel](/d/ids-tier2-geo/home-ids-tier-2-geoip-osint-intel?var-device=.*) | [⚙️ Engine System Health](/d/ids-system-health/home-ids-tier-2-engine-system-health?var-device=.*)"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "title": "ℹ️ Guide: Infrastructure Pipeline Health",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 2 },
      "transparent": true,
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### ⚙️ Infrastructure Pipeline Health\nMonitors the physical health and throughput of your Python engine, SQLite databases, and Zeek collectors.\n* 🟢 **Normal:** Pipeline Lag is < 2 seconds. Zeek Status is ONLINE. Alert Backlog is 0.\n* 🔴 **Abnormal:** High Pipeline Lag means the database is locked. A rising Alert Backlog means the script has lost internet or Telegram API connection and is caching alerts in RAM."
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Zeek NDR Status",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 4, "x": 0, "y": 6 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${PROMETHEUS_DS}" },
      "targets": [ { "expr": "home_ids_zeek_status", "legendFormat": "Status" } ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "color": { "mode": "thresholds" }, "mappings": [ { "type": "value", "options": { "1": { "text": "ONLINE", "color": "green" }, "0": { "text": "OFFLINE", "color": "red" } } } ] } }
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "IPS Mitigation Armed",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 4, "x": 4, "y": 6 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${PROMETHEUS_DS}" },
      "targets": [ { "expr": "home_ids_ips_enabled", "legendFormat": "Status" } ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "color": { "mode": "thresholds" }, "mappings": [ { "type": "value", "options": { "1": { "text": "ARMED", "color": "blue" }, "0": { "text": "DISABLED", "color": "orange" } } } ] } }
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Pipeline Lag (DB Sync)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 4, "x": 8, "y": 6 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${PROMETHEUS_DS}" },
      "targets": [ { "expr": "home_ids_collector_lag_seconds", "legendFormat": "Lag" } ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "s", "thresholds": { "mode": "absolute", "steps": [ { "value": 0, "color": "green" }, { "value": 5, "color": "yellow" }, { "value": 15, "color": "red" } ] } } }
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Pipeline Events Per Sec (EPS)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 4, "x": 12, "y": 6 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${PROMETHEUS_DS}" },
      "targets": [ { "expr": "rate(home_ids_events_processed_total[10m]) * 60", "legendFormat": "DNS/min" } ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "color": { "mode": "thresholds", "steps": [ { "value": 0, "color": "blue" } ] } } }
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Pipeline Alerts Fired (1h)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 4, "x": 16, "y": 6 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${PROMETHEUS_DS}" },
      "targets": [ { "expr": "increase(home_ids_alerts_total[1h])", "legendFormat": "Alerts" } ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "color": { "mode": "thresholds", "steps": [ { "value": 0, "color": "green" }, { "value": 1, "color": "orange" } ] } } }
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Alert Delivery Backlog",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 4, "x": 20, "y": 6 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${PROMETHEUS_DS}" },
      "targets": [ { "expr": "home_ids_alert_queue_size", "legendFormat": "Queued" } ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "thresholds": { "mode": "absolute", "steps": [ { "value": 0, "color": "green" }, { "value": 5, "color": "orange" }, { "value": 20, "color": "red" } ] } } }
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "title": "ℹ️ Guide: Macro Threat Overview",
      "gridPos": { "h": 5, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 10 },
      "transparent": true,
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### 🌍 Macro Threat Overview\nA 30,000-foot view of your entire network ecosystem.\n* **Live Baseline Breaches:** Counts how many devices are currently violating their own historical bandwidth/query limits.\n* **Anti-Poison Freezes:** Shows how many devices are currently blocked from updating their machine-learning baselines because they are exhibiting active threat behaviors (prevents malware from teaching the AI that malware is 'normal').\n* **Severe Threats:** Active devices with an aggregated risk score ≥ 6.0."
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Active Devices Monitored",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 4, "x": 0, "y": 15 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${PROMETHEUS_DS}" },
      "targets": [ { "expr": "count(home_ids_risk_score) or vector(0)", "legendFormat": "Devices" } ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "color": { "mode": "thresholds", "steps": [ { "value": 0, "color": "blue" } ] } } }
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Engine Max Risk Score",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 5, "x": 4, "y": 15 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${PROMETHEUS_DS}" },
      "targets": [ { "expr": "max(home_ids_risk_score) or vector(0)", "legendFormat": "Max Risk" } ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "thresholds": { "mode": "absolute", "steps": [ { "value": 0, "color": "green" }, { "value": 4, "color": "orange" }, { "value": 6, "color": "red" } ] } } }
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Severe Threats (Risk ≥ 6.0)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 5, "x": 9, "y": 15 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${PROMETHEUS_DS}" },
      "targets": [ { "expr": "count(home_ids_risk_score >= 6.0) or vector(0)", "legendFormat": "Threats" } ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "thresholds": { "mode": "absolute", "steps": [ { "value": 0, "color": "green" }, { "value": 1, "color": "red" } ] } } }
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Live Baseline Breaches",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 5, "x": 14, "y": 15 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${PROMETHEUS_DS}" },
      "targets": [ { "expr": "count(home_ids_query_rate > home_ids_query_rate_threshold_limit) or vector(0)", "legendFormat": "Breaches" } ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "thresholds": { "mode": "absolute", "steps": [ { "value": 0, "color": "green" }, { "value": 1, "color": "orange" }, { "value": 3, "color": "red" } ] } } }
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Anti-Poison Freezes",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 5, "x": 19, "y": 15 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${PROMETHEUS_DS}" },
      "targets": [ { "expr": "count(home_ids_baseline_poisoned == 1) or vector(0)", "legendFormat": "Frozen Nodes" } ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "thresholds": { "mode": "absolute", "steps": [ { "value": 0, "color": "green" }, { "value": 1, "color": "red" } ] } } }
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "title": "ℹ️ Guide: Master Threat Ledger & Incident Triage",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 19 },
      "transparent": true,
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### 🚨 Master Threat Ledger & Incident Triage\nThis table auto-sorts every device on your network by Risk Score, aggregating its AI and structural diagnostics.\n\n**Dictionary of Terms:**\n* **TI Match Flag & TI Risk:** The device queried a domain explicitly listed on a global hacker blocklist (AlienVault OTX, AbuseIPDB, VirusTotal).\n* **JA3 Malicious Hash:** Zeek caught the device making a TLS encrypted connection using the exact cryptographic fingerprint of known malware.\n* **Probation:** A yellow flag meaning the device is new and hasn't collected 24 hours of baseline data yet. Thresholds are stricter for these devices.\n* **Safe Listed:** A blue flag meaning this IP or Hostname is whitelisted in `config.json` and exempt from IPS quarantine blocks.\n\n**Action Item:** Click any Hostname to warp directly to its dedicated forensics dashboard."
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "table",
      "title": "🚨 Master Threat Ledger (Click Hostname to Investigate)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 16, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 27 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${PROMETHEUS_DS}" },
      "targets": [
        { "expr": "home_ids_risk_score", "format": "table", "instant": true, "refId": "A" },
        { "expr": "home_ids_ml_anomaly_score", "format": "table", "instant": true, "refId": "B" },
        { "expr": "home_ids_ti_risk", "format": "table", "instant": true, "refId": "C" },
        { "expr": "home_ids_ti_match", "format": "table", "instant": true, "refId": "D" },
        { "expr": "home_ids_query_rate", "format": "table", "instant": true, "refId": "E" },
        { "expr": "home_ids_query_rate_threshold_limit", "format": "table", "instant": true, "refId": "F" },
        { "expr": "home_ids_unique_domains", "format": "table", "instant": true, "refId": "G" },
        { "expr": "home_ids_blocked_ratio", "format": "table", "instant": true, "refId": "H" },
        { "expr": "home_ids_zeek_conn_count", "format": "table", "instant": true, "refId": "I" },
        { "expr": "home_ids_zeek_new_ips", "format": "table", "instant": true, "refId": "J" },
        { "expr": "home_ids_zeek_notices", "format": "table", "instant": true, "refId": "K" },
        { "expr": "home_ids_zeek_ja3_malicious", "format": "table", "instant": true, "refId": "L" },
        { "expr": "home_ids_probation_status", "format": "table", "instant": true, "refId": "M" },
        { "expr": "home_ids_safe_device", "format": "table", "instant": true, "refId": "N" }
      ],
      "transformations": [
        { "id": "joinByField", "options": { "byField": "hostname", "mode": "outer" } },
        {
          "id": "organize",
          "options": {
            "excludeByName": { "Time": true, "Time 1": true, "Time 2": true, "Time 3": true, "Time 4": true, "Time 5": true, "Time 6": true, "Time 7": true, "Time 8": true, "Time 9": true, "Time 10": true, "Time 11": true, "Time 12": true, "Time 13": true, "__name__": true, "device": true, "device_type": true, "instance": true, "job": true },
            "renameByName": {
              "hostname": "Hostname",
              "Value #A": "Live Risk",
              "Value #B": "ML Score",
              "Value #C": "TI Threat",
              "Value #D": "TI Match Flag",
              "Value #E": "Queries/Min",
              "Value #F": "Baseline Limit",
              "Value #G": "Unique Domains",
              "Value #H": "Blocked Ratio",
              "Value #I": "Zeek Conns",
              "Value #J": "Zeek New IPs",
              "Value #K": "Zeek Notices",
              "Value #L": "JA3 Hash",
              "Value #M": "Probation",
              "Value #N": "Safe Listed"
            }
          }
        },
        { "id": "sortBy", "options": { "fields": [ { "desc": true, "displayName": "Live Risk" } ] } }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": { "custom": { "align": "center" } },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "Hostname" },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "links",
                "value": [
                  { "title": "📈 Open Forensic Room: AI Behavioral & DGA Diagnostics", "url": "/d/ids-tier2-dns/home-ids-tier-2-dns-ml-diagnostics?var-device=${__data.fields.Hostname}", "targetBlank": true },
                  { "title": "🔒 Open Forensic Room: Zeek NDR & Network Exfiltration", "url": "/d/ids-tier2-ndr/home-ids-tier-2-network-lateral-zeek-ndr?var-device=${__data.fields.Hostname}", "targetBlank": true },
                  { "title": "🌍 Open Forensic Room: GeoIP Matrix & OSINT Mapping", "url": "/d/ids-tier2-geo/home-ids-tier-2-geoip-osint-intel?var-device=${__data.fields.Hostname}", "targetBlank": true },
                  { "title": "🪵 Open Forensic Room: Streamed Loki Logs Audit", "url": "/explore?orgId=1&left=%5B%22now-3h%22,%22now%22,%22${LOKI_DS}%22,%7B%22expr%22:%22%7Bjob%3D\\\"home_ids_alerts\\\"%7D%20%7C%20json%20%7C%20device_hostname%3D\\\"${__data.fields.Hostname}\\\"%22%7D%5D", "targetBlank": true }
                ]
              },
              { "id": "custom.align", "value": "left" }
            ]
          },
          { "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "Live Risk" }, "properties": [ { "id": "color", "value": { "mode": "thresholds", "steps": [ { "color": "green", "value": 0 }, { "color": "orange", "value": 4 }, { "color": "red", "value": 6 } ] } } ] },
          { "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "ML Score" }, "properties": [ { "id": "color", "value": { "mode": "thresholds", "steps": [ { "color": "green", "value": 0 }, { "color": "red", "value": 0.05 } ] } } ] },
          { "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "TI Threat" }, "properties": [ { "id": "color", "value": { "mode": "thresholds", "steps": [ { "color": "green", "value": 0 }, { "color": "red", "value": 0.5 } ] } } ] },
          { "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "TI Match Flag" }, "properties": [ { "id": "color", "value": { "mode": "thresholds", "steps": [ { "color": "green", "value": 0 }, { "color": "red", "value": 1 } ] } } ] },
          { "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "JA3 Hash" }, "properties": [ { "id": "color", "value": { "mode": "thresholds", "steps": [ { "color": "green", "value": 0 }, { "color": "red", "value": 1 } ] } } ] },
          { "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "Zeek Notices" }, "properties": [ { "id": "color", "value": { "mode": "thresholds", "steps": [ { "color": "green", "value": 0 }, { "color": "red", "value": 1 } ] } } ] },
          { "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "Probation" }, "properties": [ { "id": "color", "value": { "mode": "thresholds", "steps": [ { "color": "green", "value": 0 }, { "color": "orange", "value": 1 } ] } } ] },
          { "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "Safe Listed" }, "properties": [ { "id": "color", "value": { "mode": "thresholds", "steps": [ { "color": "transparent", "value": 0 }, { "color": "blue", "value": 1 } ] } } ] },
          { "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "Blocked Ratio" }, "properties": [ { "id": "color", "value": { "mode": "thresholds", "steps": [ { "color": "green", "value": 0 }, { "color": "yellow", "value": 0.5 }, { "color": "red", "value": 0.8 } ] } } ] }
        ]
      }
    }
  ]
}